# Walkthrough: Multi-UAV 6 İHA Simülasyonu

## Yapılan Değişiklikler

### Mimari

```
Gazebo (yunuseli dünyası)
├── advanced_plane × 5  (hedef — inst 0..4)
└── advanced_plane_cam × 1  (avcı — inst 5)

PX4 SITL × 6 → MAVROS × 6
├── /uav1..uav5/mavros/  (hedef İHA'lar)
└── /hunter/mavros/       (avcı İHA)
```

### Port Tablosu

| İHA | Inst | Send | Listen | MAVROS fcu_url |
|------|------|------|--------|---------------|
| uav1 | 0 | 14540 | 14580 | `udp://:14540@127.0.0.1:14580` |
| uav2 | 1 | 14541 | 14581 | `udp://:14541@127.0.0.1:14581` |
| uav3 | 2 | 14542 | 14582 | `udp://:14542@127.0.0.1:14582` |
| uav4 | 3 | 14543 | 14583 | `udp://:14543@127.0.0.1:14583` |
| uav5 | 4 | 14544 | 14584 | `udp://:14544@127.0.0.1:14584` |
| hunter | 5 | 14545 | 14585 | `udp://:14545@127.0.0.1:14585` |

